 ненадлежащего выполнения обращения в отношении ЖСК № 944 будут применены меры административного воздействия.</p><p>Приложение: уведомление.</p>","author_name":"Администрация Невского района","performer":null,"response_performers":[],"files":[{"id":18446545,"url":"/storage/2/82eaeca7-4543-4173-a7ca-8e1fe6123617.pdf","original_name":"Увед.  от 30.03.2021  по проблеме № 3290585 граффити.pdf"}],"photos":[{"id":18446546,"url":"/storage/2/cbce3c87-01d1-4c7e-b13b-69a715cceccb.png","original_name":"Screenshot_2021-03-30 Почта Mail ru отправка.png","thumbnail":"/media/cache/36/14/361487001d914b0ed7a593de82977b29.png","size":"1362x592"}],"reject":null,"interim_date":"2021-05-10"},"meta":{"title":"Ответ","icon_text":"ПО","icon_title":"Промежуточный ответ","bg_color":"#E3F2FD","border_color":"#536DFE","status_font_color":"#FFFFFF","status_bg_color":"#A5D6A7","icon_bg_color":"#536DFE"},"content_type":28},{"widget":"public.status","key":"changestatus_13455210","payload":{"id":13455210,"dt":"2021-03-24T16:32:08.901445","status_name":"Рассмотрение","status":3},"meta":{"title":"Изменение статуса сообщения","bg_color":"#EEEEEE","icon":"fa-clock-o","icon_bg_color":"#FCAA62"},"content_type":30},{"widget":"public.status","key":"changestatus_13450818","payload":{"id":13450818,"dt":"2021-03-24T10:51:11.051871","status_name":"Модерация","status":1},"meta":{"title":"Изменение статуса сообщения","bg_color":"#EEEEEE","icon":"fa-hand-paper-o","icon_bg_color":"#469ED3"},"content_type":30},{"widget":"public.petition","key":"petition_3645353","payload":{"id":3645353,"dt":"2021-03-24T10:51:10.911792","status_name":"Получен ответ","body":[{"text":"Граффити на рольставнях","typeof":1}],"photos":[{"url":"/storage/1/4e3c87f7-5b3e-433d-b10d-46656d2b81bc.jpg","original_name":"image0.jpg","id":4126273,"thumbnail":"/media/cache/25/a8/25a88e22d84204631be0f66df101de41.jpg","original_url":"/storage/1/4e3c87f7-5b3e-433d-b10d-46656d2b81bc.jpg","size":"1024x1365"},{"url":"/storage/1/2a919ae3-a8a7-4f38-81b0-c6d